% ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
% Field reference (delete this block once you understand it):
%   abbr        -> small tag shown on the left (journal short name)
%   selected    -> {true} makes it appear in the "selected papers" list on the homepage
%   arxiv       -> just the number, e.g. 2501.01234 -> renders an arXiv button
%   doi         -> DOI string -> renders a DOI link
%   abstract    -> collapsible abstract button
%   preview     -> filename in assets/img/publication_preview/ for a thumbnail
%   pdf / html  -> file in assets/pdf/ or a URL -> download / link buttons
%   bibtex_show -> {true} adds a "Bib" button showing the BibTeX entry
% See docs/CUSTOMIZE.md "Adding a new publication" for the full list.
% ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
